WEBVTT

00:00:00.249 --> 00:00:01.389
-al,

00:00:01.412 --> 00:00:03.262
TAPE numer finf.

00:00:04.467 --> 00:00:13.387
azoy hot, in, beys ir zayt shoyn geven in, BERGEN-BELSEN, hot ir shoyn gehert, shoyn, m'hot shoyn gezogt az darfn, me da- di, s'kumen on di bafrayer.

00:00:13.275 --> 00:00:14.281
yo.

00:00:13.528 --> 00:00:15.294
vos iz forgekumen vayter?

00:00:15.334 --> 00:00:17.538
vos hot forgekumen vayter?

00:00:19.030 --> 00:00:21.471
⟨v-⟩ kh'hob aykh gezogt az mir hobn gearbet.

00:00:22.472 --> 00:00:28.760
un, zey hobn, ven mir zaynen arayngegangen, mir zaynen ongekumen in BERGEN-BELSEN

00:00:28.935 --> 00:00:32.316
iz oyf yedn vant hot geven

00:00:32.316 --> 00:00:34.430
ongeshribn in rusish

00:00:34.430 --> 00:00:36.170
az dortn zaynen geven

00:00:36.170 --> 00:00:38.177
rusishe gefangene,

00:00:38.233 --> 00:00:42.817
ober ikh hob nit gekent leyenen, un keyner fun undz hot nit gekent leyenen keyn rusish.

00:00:43.093 --> 00:00:46.901
iz geven nemen mit, adresn,

00:00:47.346 --> 00:00:49.753
un s'iz geven ongetseykhnt,

00:00:50.383 --> 00:00:53.530
.. nokh dem hob ikh zikh shoyn dervust...

00:00:53.530 --> 00:00:56.598
zol men makhn a vidershtand, vayle

00:00:56.598 --> 00:01:00.064
m'vet undz alemen oyshargenen un m'vet undz oysshisn.

00:01:01.588 --> 00:01:03.286
un mir hobn geshlofn

00:01:03.310 --> 00:01:06.797
oyf dr'erd bizkl oto di o ⟨lands⟩⟨UNK⟩ vos kh'hob aykh dertseylt,

00:01:06.904 --> 00:01:09.767
un s'hot di mayz gekrokhn oyfn ponem.

00:01:10.735 --> 00:01:14.340
JUST az ir hot ongeton a shukh hot ir gefunen a mayzl

00:01:14.397 --> 00:01:15.505
in der shukh.

00:01:17.248 --> 00:01:20.330
un di badingungen dortn hot geven

00:01:20.691 --> 00:01:23.194
zeyer, zey-... s'iz geven a tsu

00:01:23.194 --> 00:01:25.531
fil mentshn evakuirt,

00:01:25.531 --> 00:01:27.806
fun andere lagern mistame oykh.

00:01:28.437 --> 00:01:32.261
un poshet, zey hobn shoyn a bisl moyre gehat, vayl zey hobn mistame gevust,

00:01:32.385 --> 00:01:35.399
hobn zey zikh baruikt a bisl mit di shlogn.

00:01:35.457 --> 00:01:38.168
vos nor zey hobn geton far FUN

00:01:38.427 --> 00:01:39.669
iz hobn zey

00:01:41.143 --> 00:01:44.177
zikh getshepet, ir veyst dokh, tsu eynem,

00:01:44.177 --> 00:01:48.325
im tseshlogn, im,... ober nisht azoy tsu alemen.

00:01:50.830 --> 00:01:54.080
ober ven mir hobn getrogn dem esn

00:01:54.660 --> 00:01:57.210
iz,... far di kinderlekh...

00:01:57.210 --> 00:02:02.006
iz... un mir flegn dortn shoyn oykhet esn, hot shoyn geven a bisl besere esn, gedikhtere;

00:02:02.006 --> 00:02:04.779
keyner hot nit, aroysgelovet di gedikhte...

00:02:05.798 --> 00:02:07.026
hobn mir gezen

00:02:07.026 --> 00:02:09.301
az di o vos...

00:02:09.645 --> 00:02:12.590
s'iz dokh geven a grenets bizkl vanen

00:02:12.590 --> 00:02:15.330
dos iz der, di froyen hobn do geven,

00:02:15.330 --> 00:02:18.059
un nokh dem der mener-lager vu mir zaynen gegangen.

00:02:18.083 --> 00:02:21.131
⟨oto,⟩ m'hot dokh nit getort arayngeyn in mener-lager.

00:02:21.492 --> 00:02:24.374
hot ir gedarft zikh bay der budkele meldn,

00:02:24.374 --> 00:02:26.593
az di o vos hot undz gefirt,

00:02:26.593 --> 00:02:29.416
dos iz di un di, un vu zi geyt, un...

00:02:30.013 --> 00:02:31.450
un oyf tsurik,

00:02:31.450 --> 00:02:33.942
ye, hobn mir shoyn gezen az di S.S.

00:02:33.942 --> 00:02:35.728
geyen vayse bendlekh

00:02:35.937 --> 00:02:37.011
oyf di hent.

00:02:38.350 --> 00:02:41.280
ober ver hot gevust? hobn mir geklert, efsher

00:02:42.771 --> 00:02:44.750
s'iz a ander bafel, od-...

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:46.683
ir hot zikh dos nisht forgeshtelt.

00:02:46.683 --> 00:02:49.987
un mir zaynen arayngekumen in lager nokh di esn,

00:02:50.398 --> 00:02:54.360
hobn zey, di mener, gelegn oyf dr'erd unter di drotn;

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:57.581
nor di kop hot geven shoyn aroysgenumen di drotn.

00:02:57.908 --> 00:02:59.319
un zey hobn geshrign,

00:02:59.781 --> 00:03:01.510
"mir zaynen shoyn bafrayt!

00:03:01.510 --> 00:03:04.160
mir sh- hobn shoyn undzer nekome!"

00:03:04.388 --> 00:03:10.340
un... mir hobn moyre gehat afile tsu kukn, vayl di S.S.-manke hot dokh undz nokh gefirt.

00:03:10.378 --> 00:03:12.610
un di vakh iz gevezn nokh dortn?

00:03:12.758 --> 00:03:15.986
oyf ahin hot geven di vakhe mit vayse bendlekh,

00:03:15.986 --> 00:03:17.159
ober oyf tsurik

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:19.333
hot men zey shoyn keynem nit gezen.

00:03:19.407 --> 00:03:21.662
m'hot shoyn zikh nit gedarft meldn.

00:03:22.208 --> 00:03:24.244
mir hobn nit gevust vos s'hot geshen.

00:03:25.279 --> 00:03:27.618
zaynen mir arayngegangen in lager,

00:03:27.928 --> 00:03:29.610
un bay nakht

00:03:30.223 --> 00:03:34.410
hobn mir gehert zeyer groyse bombardirungen.

00:03:37.429 --> 00:03:40.190
⟨hot, mir hobn⟩ zikh nisht gerirt fun lager.

00:03:41.665 --> 00:03:46.030
⟨d-⟩ ikh rekhn az zey hobn geshtelt a vidershtand oder vos; kh'hob nisht di minderste anung.

00:03:46.030 --> 00:03:48.108
tsu eroplans hobn gevorfn bombes,

00:03:48.108 --> 00:03:49.050
kh'veys nit.

00:03:49.292 --> 00:03:51.457
meydlekh zaynen aroysgelofn,

00:03:51.457 --> 00:03:53.876
ober ikh mit mayn shvester, kh'hob ir gezogt, "NO.

00:03:55.030 --> 00:03:56.509
mir geyen nisht,

00:03:56.532 --> 00:03:59.807
un oyb mir darfn umkumen, veln mir do oyfn plats umkumen."

00:04:00.700 --> 00:04:04.879
ober s'hot nokh dem geven a satisfaktsye az ir zaynt aroysgegangen,

00:04:04.918 --> 00:04:06.982
vayle ir hot gezen di S.S.

00:04:06.982 --> 00:04:09.115
in eynem oder tsvey tog...

00:04:09.475 --> 00:04:11.907
iz mir zaynen geven azoy lang,

00:04:12.276 --> 00:04:14.227
fun dray un fertsik,

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:16.641
a gantsn fir un fertsik,

00:04:16.714 --> 00:04:19.577
un a, ALMOST a halbn finf un fertsik

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.619
zaynen mir geven

00:04:21.692 --> 00:04:25.157
bay azelkhe shlekhte badingungen, un mit klep,

00:04:25.157 --> 00:04:27.744
un krankshaftn farshidene...

00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:30.241
un zey hobn zikh in eyn tog azoy geendert,

00:04:30.687 --> 00:04:32.455
di groyse

00:04:32.455 --> 00:04:34.360
BIG SHOTSes. SO...

00:04:35.918 --> 00:04:37.264
⟨hobn⟩ mir gevart,

00:04:37.264 --> 00:04:40.164
nokh dem iz arayngekumen Englender tsu undz.

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:41.964
hobn zey geredt english.

00:04:41.964 --> 00:04:43.437
ver hot gevust?

00:04:44.575 --> 00:04:47.741
ober zey hobn gevizn, umgefer, az,

00:04:48.844 --> 00:04:51.993
dos o iz, mir zaynen shoyn FREE,

00:04:52.118 --> 00:04:55.959
un, zey hobn shoyn undz ⟨o-⟩ gegebn, besere esn.

00:04:55.982 --> 00:04:59.368
halevay voltn zey nisht gegebn di esn, volt geven a sakh beser.

00:04:59.728 --> 00:05:03.265
zey hobn gegebn zeyer a sakh konservirte esn,

00:05:03.525 --> 00:05:06.838
vos s'iz geven, az ir hot geefnt a pushke, hot geven oder tshont

00:05:06.838 --> 00:05:09.057
oder fleysh farshidene,

00:05:09.057 --> 00:05:13.402
un di oysgehungerte, kranke, fardorbene

00:05:13.402 --> 00:05:16.153
STOMACHs hobn dos nit gekent nemen;

00:05:16.153 --> 00:05:18.976
m'hot gedarft hobn a laykhte dyete.

00:05:21.514 --> 00:05:23.077
un ikh,

00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:26.013
hob zikh nisht tsugekhapt tsum esn,

00:05:26.863 --> 00:05:30.522
vayl ikh hob gevust, az ikh'l zikh tsukhapn tsum esn iz...

00:05:30.522 --> 00:05:31.720
ikh hob geklert,

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:34.395
"ikh'l esn eyn portsye un mayn shvester eyn portsye,

00:05:34.395 --> 00:05:37.052
un di tsveyte portsye, efsher veln mir gefinen mayn mamen..."

00:05:37.052 --> 00:05:38.961
khotsh mir hobn gezen di krematoryes...

00:05:38.961 --> 00:05:41.592
ober ir veyst, in ayn- in ayer untergedank

00:05:41.592 --> 00:05:42.771
hot ir geklert,

00:05:42.793 --> 00:05:46.870
"ver, vos ⟨ho⟩t men ir, far vos ⟨ho⟩t men ir...? zi hot keynem nisht getshepet, zi hot keynem nisht...

00:05:47.367 --> 00:05:49.709
far vos? efsher veln mir ir gefinen."

00:05:49.709 --> 00:05:51.793
hobn mir gehaltn a por portsyes broyt,

00:05:51.793 --> 00:05:55.015
tomer, tomer ⟨vol⟩t men undz nokh a mol firn,

00:05:55.015 --> 00:05:57.638
zoln mir hobn mit vos oy- zikh oyfhaltn.

00:05:58.403 --> 00:06:01.423
⟨u-⟩ bin ikh nisht aroys un bin nisht...

00:06:01.947 --> 00:06:05.199
kh'hob zikh zeyer, zeyer gelitn, ober

00:06:05.199 --> 00:06:07.315
kh'hob zikh gehaltn fason.

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:12.576
un, m- ikh bin geven bizkl,

00:06:13.017 --> 00:06:17.010
kh'veys, efsher zeks vokhn oder vos, ot azoy, nokh dortn.

00:06:17.252 --> 00:06:20.353
nokh dem hot men undz aribergefirt

00:06:21.066 --> 00:06:22.443
in kosharn.

00:06:23.007 --> 00:06:25.988
dos iz, dortn iz geven militer.

00:06:26.483 --> 00:06:29.194
oykh in zelbn BERGEN-BELSEN?

00:06:27.951 --> 00:06:31.307
nisht BERGEN-BE- BERGEN-BELSEN,

00:06:31.307 --> 00:06:34.174
ober s'hot shoyn nit geven der lager;

00:06:34.174 --> 00:06:37.276
s'hot geven kazarmes, kosharn, vos s'iz...

00:06:35.899 --> 00:06:37.496
nor in zelbe shtot?

00:06:38.177 --> 00:06:40.044
yo, s'iz geven,

00:06:40.152 --> 00:06:42.984
kh'veys, efsher finef kilometer oder...

00:06:42.984 --> 00:06:45.040
az mir hobn dokh geWALKt tsu fus.

00:06:46.024 --> 00:06:48.110
un m'hot undz,

00:06:48.370 --> 00:06:50.844
di ershte zakh iz ariber di kranke,

00:06:51.289 --> 00:06:53.746
d- dos hot geheysn der revir,

00:06:53.746 --> 00:06:56.227
un mir zaynen mitgegangen mit di kranke.

00:06:58.123 --> 00:07:00.204
un nokh dem zaynen shoyn ongekumen

00:07:00.204 --> 00:07:01.357
di ale.

00:07:01.988 --> 00:07:05.961
hobn mir geven oyf,

00:07:06.612 --> 00:07:08.884
in a, m'hot gegebn a tsimer

00:07:09.514 --> 00:07:11.492
far fir,

00:07:12.518 --> 00:07:15.130
a gresern, un a klenern far tsvey.

00:07:15.130 --> 00:07:16.409
hobn mir genumen

00:07:16.467 --> 00:07:20.983
dem klenern tsimer, vayle mir hobn gevolt shoyn ikh mit mayn shvester zayn.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:24.611
un azoy hobn mir shoyn gezen yedn tog

00:07:25.545 --> 00:07:28.822
vi sh- me darf shoyn avekshikn transportn.

00:07:28.822 --> 00:07:31.428
di ershte zakh hot zikh ongehoybn shafn

00:07:31.789 --> 00:07:33.976
vider a JUDENRAT,

00:07:35.282 --> 00:07:38.685
vos, zey hobn geven farantvortlekh,

00:07:38.708 --> 00:07:42.753
 far, transportn vos s'vet onkumen, kranke.

00:07:42.753 --> 00:07:45.564
bay undz iz dokh nokh geven a froyen-lager,

00:07:45.564 --> 00:07:48.405
ober s'hot shoyn ongehoybn kumen mener.

00:07:49.457 --> 00:07:52.939
un, m'hot gefirt transportn azoy vi

00:07:52.939 --> 00:07:55.538
keyn Shvedn, kranke.

00:07:55.538 --> 00:07:57.416
iz hobn mir geholfn,

00:07:57.625 --> 00:07:59.239
 zey,

00:08:00.392 --> 00:08:02.287
aroys- ir veyst dokh,

00:08:02.287 --> 00:08:04.970
iberton, mir hobn gegebn zakhn,

00:08:04.970 --> 00:08:07.844
un zey, ver s'hot nisht gekent WALKn

00:08:07.986 --> 00:08:10.511
hot men arayngezetst in dem,

00:08:10.872 --> 00:08:15.415
 bus, oyf, zoln zey, m'hot zey avekgenumen keyn Shvedn.

00:08:16.187 --> 00:08:18.138
dos hot geven undzer arbet.

00:08:18.921 --> 00:08:23.235
un, mayn shvester hot gevorn a krankn-shvester,

00:08:23.460 --> 00:08:25.310
hot zi gearbet oyf revir.

00:08:26.211 --> 00:08:28.629
un ikh hob nisht gearbet oyf revir,

00:08:28.629 --> 00:08:30.300
vayl ikh bin a bisl

00:08:30.300 --> 00:08:32.617
mer veykher; kh'ken nisht farnemen.

00:08:33.433 --> 00:08:37.021
iz, ⟨hot, hob⟩ ikh zikh bakant, hob ikh gevorn

00:08:37.871 --> 00:08:41.646
a, eyner iz, hot, gekont,

00:08:41.888 --> 00:08:43.384
er hot gehat a onkl,

00:08:43.727 --> 00:08:47.930
undzerer a bakanter, vos er iz hot shoyn gemakht di JUDENRAT,

00:08:48.081 --> 00:08:50.356
vos, hot er mir gegebn dem JOB,

00:08:50.356 --> 00:08:51.872
zol ikh vern a blokove.

00:08:52.198 --> 00:08:54.976
iz fleg kumen ⟨t-⟩ farshidene transportn,

00:08:55.607 --> 00:08:57.609
un m'hot undz gegebn esn,

00:08:57.868 --> 00:09:01.451
un ikh fleg tsugebn a reshime,

00:09:01.451 --> 00:09:03.607
vifl mentshn ikh hob oyfn blok,

00:09:03.607 --> 00:09:05.439
hot men gebrengt, lomir zogn,

00:09:05.462 --> 00:09:09.337
a zekl mel, a zekl tsuker, a zekl groypn,

00:09:09.495 --> 00:09:12.357
un yeder eyner hot gehat aza ayzerne eyvele

00:09:13.275 --> 00:09:16.745
in, dortn bay im in tsimer, un m'hot zikh aleyn gekokht.

00:09:16.768 --> 00:09:18.804
ober s'iz geven a kantine oykhet,

00:09:19.198 --> 00:09:22.482
un ver s'hot gevolt hot gekent geyn esn oyf di kantine.

00:09:23.232 --> 00:09:25.791
un s'hot geheysn di koshere kantine.

00:09:26.877 --> 00:09:30.077
dos hobn di Englender gebra- gegebn aykh, di...?

00:09:29.458 --> 00:09:32.161
alts hot di Englender, ye, ye.

00:09:32.161 --> 00:09:35.038
ikh bin nit geven bay keyn andere akhuts bay di Englender.

00:09:35.517 --> 00:09:36.996
un zey hobn zikh,

00:09:37.508 --> 00:09:39.426
bagangen zeyer fayn,

00:09:39.482 --> 00:09:41.180
nor m'hot zikh ongehoybn makhn,

00:09:41.997 --> 00:09:44.387
"ver vil forn tsurik keyn Poyln?"

00:09:46.384 --> 00:09:48.622
hot men zikh gedarft registrirn.

00:09:49.118 --> 00:09:54.246
"ver vil forn,", lomir zogn, "keyn Ungarn, keyn, Budapest, keyn...?"

00:09:54.246 --> 00:09:56.216
vu fun vanen eyner hot gekumen.

00:09:56.948 --> 00:09:58.444
ikh hob bashlosn

00:09:58.669 --> 00:10:02.156
az ikh zits do bay di Englender vifl s'vet zikh lozn.

00:10:03.411 --> 00:10:04.957
IN THE MEANTIME

00:10:05.402 --> 00:10:08.022
hot mayn tate

00:10:08.022 --> 00:10:11.461
do gehat dray shvester in Amerike, vos

00:10:11.461 --> 00:10:13.108
kh'hob gevust fun zey, ober mir,

00:10:13.485 --> 00:10:17.135
kh'vil nit geyn tsu dem ⟨onheyb, mir iz⟩ nit geven farbindung mit zey,

00:10:17.135 --> 00:10:19.330
vayle mayn tate hot dokh nit gelebt.

00:10:20.674 --> 00:10:23.236
ober ven m'hot gedarft forn keyn Amerike,

00:10:23.236 --> 00:10:24.853
hot geven do

00:10:25.230 --> 00:10:27.547
yidishe bokherimlekh

00:10:27.547 --> 00:10:29.746
vos zaynen geven fun undzer shtot.

00:10:30.394 --> 00:10:32.030
un fun undzer shtot

00:10:32.030 --> 00:10:33.459
hot zikh gegrindet

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.197
a kolektiv,

00:10:35.845 --> 00:10:38.994
hobn zey geheysn der Pruzhener kolektiv,

00:10:39.388 --> 00:10:42.761
in Feldafing. dos iz geven Minkhn.

00:10:42.761 --> 00:10:46.622
dos iz geven di vos zaynen bafrayt gevorn durkh di Amerikaner.

00:10:47.151 --> 00:10:48.309
in MÜNCHEN?

00:10:48.467 --> 00:10:51.431
NO, in Feldafing. s'iz geven lebn Minkhn.

00:10:51.623 --> 00:10:55.776
ikh hob ge- d- geven dokh in BERGEN-BELSEN,

00:10:56.196 --> 00:10:59.930
ober mir hobn zikh dervust durkh di yinglekh

00:10:59.930 --> 00:11:02.553
az mayn bruder hot ibergelebt.

00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:05.753
bokherim vos m'hot gevandert

00:11:05.967 --> 00:11:08.880
hobn zikh getsoygn tsurik keyn Pruzhene,

00:11:09.713 --> 00:11:12.474
un er hot zikh getsoygn tsurik keyn Pruzhene.

00:11:13.662 --> 00:11:14.753
hobn zey im,

00:11:14.961 --> 00:11:18.819
durkh mentshn, ir veyst dokh az unter vegns hot men zikh dervust

00:11:19.382 --> 00:11:22.045
az in Pruzhene iz farbrent gevorn

00:11:22.045 --> 00:11:24.922
un ir kent tsurik nisht forn keyn Pruzhene.

00:11:24.922 --> 00:11:26.868
hobn zey zikh umgekert.

00:11:27.263 --> 00:11:30.092
m'hot im gebrengt in Feldafing,

00:11:30.823 --> 00:11:35.710
in dem kolektiv vu di Pruzhener hobn organizirt.

00:11:35.717 --> 00:11:38.985
dos heyst, er hot geven oyf di Amerikaner zone.

00:11:41.472 --> 00:11:43.980
ikh hob zikh dervust...

00:11:44.239 --> 00:11:47.839
NO, di mener hobn zikh dervust az ikh un mayn shvester

00:11:47.839 --> 00:11:49.869
un nokh a por Pruzhener

00:11:50.787 --> 00:11:52.418
voynen zikh

00:11:52.812 --> 00:11:54.291
in BERGEN-BELSEN.

00:11:54.634 --> 00:11:56.248
zaynen zey gekumen

00:11:56.271 --> 00:11:57.676
un zey hobn gevolt,

00:11:57.676 --> 00:11:59.522
zoln mir ariberforn

00:12:00.372 --> 00:12:01.699
keyn Feldafing.

00:12:02.194 --> 00:12:05.030
ikh hob gezogt, "ikh rir zikh nisht fun danen.

00:12:05.704 --> 00:12:07.397
kh'veys nit vos s'vet zayn.

00:12:07.397 --> 00:12:09.498
kh'vil zikh arumkukn un zen.

00:12:09.498 --> 00:12:11.571
kh'darf kumen tsu mayne koykhes, vos..."

00:12:12.049 --> 00:12:14.422
hob ikh mit mayn shvester geblibn,

00:12:14.648 --> 00:12:16.273
un a por meydlekh

00:12:16.273 --> 00:12:19.938
vos zey hobn, geven nokh geb- ibergelebt, fun undzer shtot...

00:12:19.938 --> 00:12:21.850
layder, keyner hot shoyn nit geblibn

00:12:21.850 --> 00:12:23.788
akhuts ikh mit mayn shvester...

00:12:24.722 --> 00:12:27.855
zaynen zey avekgeforn mit di mener.

00:12:28.789 --> 00:12:31.584
un azoy hobn mir shoyn gehat farbindung,

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:34.992
vos, s'iz geven zeyer shver;

00:12:35.134 --> 00:12:39.127
az ir hot geforn, az ir hot geforn fun BERGEN-BELSEN

00:12:39.454 --> 00:12:43.399
keyn, keyn, Feldafing,

00:12:43.504 --> 00:12:45.686
hot nokh nit geven keyn TRAINs,

00:12:45.686 --> 00:12:49.134
hot ir gedarft forn oyf azelkhe vagonen, zikh shlepn,

00:12:49.225 --> 00:12:53.336
vos m'hot gefirt koyln oder andere TOWAROWe vagonen.

00:12:53.680 --> 00:12:56.503
ober ONCE IN A WHILE hobn mir geforn,

00:12:56.503 --> 00:12:59.177
un mir hobn zikh registrirt dortn.

00:12:59.177 --> 00:13:01.385
far vos hobn mir zikh registrirt dortn?

00:13:01.442 --> 00:13:03.241
vayle mir hobn gevolt,

00:13:03.737 --> 00:13:07.224
az mir veln z- vern in farbindung mit undzere tantes,

00:13:07.348 --> 00:13:09.805
efsher zoln mir khotsh bay imetsn hobn

00:13:09.998 --> 00:13:12.915
tsvey, azoy vi,

00:13:13.423 --> 00:13:15.459
s'volt keyner dokh,

00:13:15.718 --> 00:13:17.900
⟨m-⟩ azoy vi shteyner zaynen mir geven:

00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:21.083
nit keyn mishpokhe, nit keyn mamen, nit keynem.

00:13:21.083 --> 00:13:22.529
nit keyn landslayt.

00:13:23.059 --> 00:13:25.078
hobn mir zikh dortn registrirt.

00:13:27.126 --> 00:13:28.672
un,

00:13:28.847 --> 00:13:31.608
mir flegn nor kumen ONCE IN A WHILE.

00:13:32.104 --> 00:13:35.726
hobn mir aribergenumen dem bruder... er hot dokh shoyn geven registrirt...

00:13:35.918 --> 00:13:37.937
keyn BERGEN-BELSEN,

00:13:38.010 --> 00:13:42.194
un er hot geven in BERGEN-BELSEN, iz er geven mer toyt vi lebedik.

00:13:42.313 --> 00:13:44.720
er hot geven zeyer a kranker,

00:13:44.912 --> 00:13:46.851
UNK vos er hot ibergelebt.

00:13:47.933 --> 00:13:49.999
hobn mir im khasene gemakht,

00:13:50.751 --> 00:13:52.432
ikh mit mayn shvester.

00:13:52.573 --> 00:13:55.582
un vos me fleg gebn, di konservn, ir veyst dokh,

00:13:55.582 --> 00:13:57.717
 di TUNA fish, di hoykhe pushkes,

00:13:57.717 --> 00:14:01.561
hobn mir opgekokht fish, mir hobn arayngeladn a por mentshn,

00:14:01.922 --> 00:14:03.755
un mir hobn gevorn,

00:14:04.723 --> 00:14:06.749
shoyn ⟨mir hobn⟩ gemakht a khasene.

00:14:08.065 --> 00:14:11.467
IN THE MEANTIME iz, ikh hob zikh oykh bakant mit eynem.

00:14:12.267 --> 00:14:14.640
iz, hot men im geshosn.

00:14:15.726 --> 00:14:18.364
vayl mir hobn geklert, "vos veln mir forn, tsvey meydlekh

00:14:18.364 --> 00:14:20.330
aleyn in der velt, Amerike,

00:14:20.330 --> 00:14:23.516
nit keyn shprakh un nisht keynem? di tantes, ver veys?"

00:14:23.843 --> 00:14:28.194
oyser vos mir hobn shoyn gehert fun di o ⟨s-,⟩ soldatn,

00:14:28.194 --> 00:14:31.796
azoy vi di tantes zaynen zeyer orem un a kind halt zey oys.

00:14:31.796 --> 00:14:33.607
hobn mir shoyn gezen di lage.

00:14:34.002 --> 00:14:36.358
un mir hobn bashlosn, efsher veln mir forn

00:14:36.381 --> 00:14:39.868
keyn Yisroel, vayl dos iz dokh geven undzer DREAM.

00:14:42.625 --> 00:14:45.842
 IN THE MEANTIME hobn mir oysgezukht in Yisroel

00:14:45.966 --> 00:14:48.508
undzer a shokhn vos mir hobn im geholfn,

00:14:49.375 --> 00:14:53.959
er hot geven in a kibuts un mir hobn im geholfn ariberforn nokh Yisroel,

00:14:54.201 --> 00:14:56.712
un mir hobn geholfn tsu batsoln...

00:14:56.712 --> 00:14:58.855
er hot gemakht a fiktsye mit a meydl,

00:14:58.855 --> 00:15:00.880
vos yener tate hot getsolt far

00:15:00.880 --> 00:15:02.296
a halbn sertifikat.

00:15:02.296 --> 00:15:04.643
ir vey- ikh veys nit tsu far aykh iz azoy bakant

00:15:04.643 --> 00:15:07.000
di ale shtik vos,

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:10.226
dos iz hot nokh geven a sakh frier vi ir zaynt gekumen aher,

00:15:10.519 --> 00:15:13.981
ober mir hobn gehat undzere kombinatsyes.

00:15:14.232 --> 00:15:16.301
un er hot geven in Yisroel,

00:15:16.543 --> 00:15:20.750
un mir hobn zikh shoyn farshtendikt mit im, un er fleg shraybn tsu undz.

00:15:20.750 --> 00:15:22.258
hot er geshribn azoy:

00:15:22.467 --> 00:15:23.777
"mayne kinder,

00:15:24.323 --> 00:15:26.494
ikh voyn zikh in a kibuts

00:15:26.719 --> 00:15:30.071
in HAGALIL HAELYON, MESHEK DAFNA."

00:15:30.634 --> 00:15:32.872
s'iz geven a linker kibuts.

00:15:33.520 --> 00:15:36.922
"un, ikh vil aykh zen

00:15:36.928 --> 00:15:38.846
mit mayn gantse hartsn,

00:15:39.072 --> 00:15:42.137
ober az ir vet zikh aynordenen in Amerike,

00:15:42.177 --> 00:15:43.431
un ir vet kenen,

00:15:43.431 --> 00:15:45.309
vet ir kumen keyn Yisroel,

00:15:45.754 --> 00:15:48.249
far, tsu bazukh."

00:15:48.927 --> 00:15:51.435
un mir hobn nit farshtanen vos er hot gemeynt.

00:15:51.435 --> 00:15:53.409
un mir hobn nokh geshribn nokh a mol,

00:15:53.533 --> 00:15:56.145
"du tsebrekhst undzere gedanken, un..."

00:15:56.145 --> 00:15:57.881
hot er undz geshribn ofn:

00:15:58.579 --> 00:16:00.260
"fort keyn Amerike;

00:16:00.452 --> 00:16:02.521
ir hot dortn oykhet mishpokhe.

00:16:03.169 --> 00:16:07.266
un az ir vet nit kenen zayn in Amerike, ir vet zikh nit kenen aynordenen,

00:16:07.266 --> 00:16:10.157
iz Yisroel far aykh shtendik ofn di toyern."

00:16:10.645 --> 00:16:15.026
hobn mir gekoyft a fridzhider far im, mir hobn avekgeshikt in kibuts.

00:16:15.437 --> 00:16:20.231
mir hobn gekoyft, a STOVE, a oyvn,

00:16:20.618 --> 00:16:22.925
un mir hobn avekgeshikt un mir hobn geklert,

00:16:22.925 --> 00:16:24.985
"oyb s'vet undz nisht gelingen mit Amerike,

00:16:24.985 --> 00:16:27.699
dervayl vet dos zayn in kibuts, un nokh dem ⟨mir veln⟩ kumen,

00:16:27.722 --> 00:16:29.825
veln mir dortn dos farkoyfn,

00:16:29.967 --> 00:16:34.196
un mir veln, far di gelt nemen a dire oder vos."

00:16:35.434 --> 00:16:38.583
ober s'iz nisht, ⟨d-⟩ der

00:16:38.607 --> 00:16:41.402
lebn iz nisht vi ir kent oysplanen.

00:16:42.100 --> 00:16:44.422
zaynen mir geven in BERGEN-BELSEN,

00:16:45.103 --> 00:16:46.464
un mir hobn gearbet,

00:16:46.690 --> 00:16:49.090
un a bisl hot men tsugehandlt.

00:16:49.556 --> 00:16:53.737
mayn shvester hot gearbet oyfn revir; me flegt undz gebn tsuteylungen.

00:16:53.895 --> 00:16:59.981
hobn mir farkoyft di tsuteylungen, un mir hobn gekoyft andere zakhn vos mir hobn gevolt.

00:17:01.033 --> 00:17:03.173
un ikh hob zikh bakant mit a bokher,

00:17:03.173 --> 00:17:07.074
un, er hot mir geholfn khasene makhn mayn bruder.

00:17:07.074 --> 00:17:09.290
hot er gezogt, a zeyer, geven zeyer a religyezer,

00:17:09.290 --> 00:17:11.488
⟨gezogt⟩, "tsum ersht veln mir khasene makhn ⟨a eltern⟩,

00:17:11.512 --> 00:17:13.210
un nokh dem veln mir."

00:17:13.217 --> 00:17:15.315
dervayl hot er gegangen tsu a MATCH.

00:17:15.315 --> 00:17:17.631
di polyakn hobn geshpilt mit di yidn,

00:17:17.772 --> 00:17:20.727
un di yidn hobn gevunen

00:17:20.727 --> 00:17:22.457
un di polyakn hobn farlorn.

00:17:23.393 --> 00:17:25.800
iz, hot men im geshosn,

00:17:27.105 --> 00:17:28.761
un ikh hob gekl-...

00:17:27.308 --> 00:17:29.074
dos iz gevezn in Poyln?

00:17:29.265 --> 00:17:32.802
in BERGEN-BELSEN hot dos geven! ver redt fun Poyln?

00:17:32.860 --> 00:17:35.371
NEVER hob ikh zikh tsurikgekert keyn Poyln,

00:17:35.371 --> 00:17:39.485
akhuts vos ikh bin geforn in AUSCHWITZ nokh a mol tsu bazukhn.

00:17:40.453 --> 00:17:44.170
un kh'hob shoyn gedarft loyfn in shpitol. er hot geven a frumer;

00:17:44.170 --> 00:17:46.963
er hot nit gevolt esn, fun der kukhnye.

00:17:46.963 --> 00:17:48.581
hob ikh gedarft kokhn.

00:17:48.688 --> 00:17:51.056
s'hot nisht geven laykht far mir.

00:17:52.536 --> 00:17:56.227
hobn mir... dervayle hot men im avekgeshikt

00:17:56.468 --> 00:17:58.807
in a sanatoryum in di SCHWEIZ.

00:17:59.438 --> 00:18:02.537
un er hot gezogt az mir veln zikh trefn in Yisroel,

00:18:02.779 --> 00:18:04.477
ober azoy vi kh'hob gezen:

00:18:04.517 --> 00:18:07.499
er iz krank, un ikh ⟨hob⟩ azoy fil adurkhgemakht.

00:18:08.668 --> 00:18:10.445
hot men gelitn a bisl,

00:18:10.445 --> 00:18:12.357
un m'hot gemakht a shlus.

00:18:14.524 --> 00:18:17.602
un, kh'bin

00:18:17.967 --> 00:18:19.929
geven in Amerike,

00:18:19.929 --> 00:18:22.938
ikh bin z- kh'hob zikh registrirt in Amerike,

00:18:22.945 --> 00:18:25.774
un kh'hob zikh shoyn oyfgeshribn mit mayne tantes.

00:18:27.467 --> 00:18:29.050
un in,

00:18:29.050 --> 00:18:30.852
nayn un fertsik,

00:18:31.602 --> 00:18:35.933
hob ikh shoyn gekrign azoy vi ikh, mir kenen forn keyn Amerike.

00:18:36.276 --> 00:18:37.434
iz in

00:18:37.812 --> 00:18:39.831
AUGUST nayn un fertsik...

00:18:39.837 --> 00:18:41.908
di DATEs veys ikh ven,

00:18:41.908 --> 00:18:44.741
ober vu ikh bin alts adurkhgegangen, gedenk ikh nisht...

00:18:45.186 --> 00:18:46.631
zaynen mir

00:18:47.413 --> 00:18:49.111
gerufn gevorn

00:18:49.303 --> 00:18:54.072
un m'hot undz bashtetikt, mir hobn adurkhgegangen di ale formulatsyes,

00:18:54.282 --> 00:18:57.971
un mir zaynen avekgeforn keyn Bremen, ikh mit mayn shvester,

00:18:58.450 --> 00:19:01.161
un mir zaynen ongekumen keyn Amerike.

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:02.952
iz di o tante

00:19:02.952 --> 00:19:04.805
vos hot gedarft undz,

00:19:04.828 --> 00:19:06.610
mir hobn gedarft kumen tsu ir,

00:19:07.663 --> 00:19:09.997
iz hot undz gekumen a telegrame

00:19:09.997 --> 00:19:13.040
az Beyle Siskin, ROSS STREET,

00:19:13.452 --> 00:19:15.386
 MARCY AVENUE,

00:19:15.730 --> 00:19:16.922
SHE DIED.

00:19:17.299 --> 00:19:19.160
dos iz geven in der telegrame.

00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:21.410
⟨hobn mir⟩ shoyn ongehoybn veynen: vos zol men ton?

00:19:22.530 --> 00:19:26.304
mir zaynen ongekumen, hot undz opgenumen der H.I.A.S.

00:19:27.222 --> 00:19:29.277
nokh tsvey tantes hobn mir gehat:

00:19:29.277 --> 00:19:31.654
eyne iz geven in,

00:19:32.082 --> 00:19:35.897
 in, Bruklin hot zikh gevoynt,

00:19:35.897 --> 00:19:37.914
un eyne hot zikh gevoynt in Filadelfye.

00:19:39.068 --> 00:19:44.388
hot zi undz nisht gekumen opnemen, un mir hobn nisht gekent farshteyn far vos ⟨hot zi⟩ undz nisht gekent opkumen,

00:19:44.388 --> 00:19:46.303
nor mir hobn shoyn gevorn farbitert,

00:19:46.303 --> 00:19:48.067
mayn shvester hot gekhalesht...

00:19:48.067 --> 00:19:49.051
der sof,

00:19:49.108 --> 00:19:50.531
MAKEn kurts,

00:19:50.531 --> 00:19:53.366
zi hot undz ariberge- m'hot undz aribergenumen,

00:19:53.366 --> 00:19:55.650
der H.I.A.S. hot undz aribergenumen,

00:19:55.892 --> 00:20:00.613
un zey hobn, un mir zaynen geven in H.I.A.S., kh'rekhn, efsher a monat.

00:20:01.562 --> 00:20:03.277
un dem ershtn tog,

00:20:03.587 --> 00:20:06.770
vi nor mir zaynen aroys, hobn mir shoyn getrofn mentshn

00:20:06.793 --> 00:20:09.588
vos zaynen frier fun undz geven in H.I.A.S.,

00:20:10.354 --> 00:20:14.364
un zey hobn undz gezogt, "veynts nit un klogts nit!

00:20:14.590 --> 00:20:16.727
ayer mishpokhe vet kumen,

00:20:16.817 --> 00:20:18.127
ir vet zen."

00:20:18.724 --> 00:20:20.371
un s'iz geven azoy.

00:20:20.884 --> 00:20:23.011
der H.I.A.S. hot undz bazorgt

00:20:23.011 --> 00:20:25.851
mit a FURNISHED ROOM, zoln mir RENTn bay imetsn,

00:20:25.851 --> 00:20:28.101
zoln mir nit zitsn in H.I.A.S.

00:20:29.473 --> 00:20:33.840
un zey hobn getsolt, kh'veys, efsher tsvey khadoshim oder dray khadoshim... kh'hob nisht keyn anung...

00:20:33.895 --> 00:20:36.624
bizkl mir zaynen avekgegangen arbetn.

00:20:39.227 --> 00:20:40.891
m⟨UNK⟩ on a shprakh,

00:20:41.185 --> 00:20:43.897
on gelt, on gornisht;

00:20:44.425 --> 00:20:47.169
nor vos s'hot shoyn ongevoksn a bisl hor oyfn kop.

00:20:47.749 --> 00:20:49.565
hot men avekgegangen

00:20:50.027 --> 00:20:54.886
un ⟨t-⟩ v- tsu vos hob ikh zikh gekent nemen? hob ikh gevorn bay RIPLEY CLOTHES,

00:20:55.140 --> 00:20:56.732
ikh hob ongehoybn arbetn,

00:20:56.732 --> 00:21:00.999
un kh'hob gevorn a FINISHER, un kh'hob fardint.

00:21:01.317 --> 00:21:04.098
hobn mir shoyn di ershte zikh aroysgetrotn fun dem H.I.A.S.,

00:21:04.098 --> 00:21:06.154
vayl undz hot geven zeyer paynlekh.

00:21:06.278 --> 00:21:08.921
bay undz hot dos geheysn az me git undz a nedove,

00:21:09.535 --> 00:21:11.503
un mir hobn gehat tsu fil

00:21:11.830 --> 00:21:15.435
shtolts, az imetser zol undz helfn; mir zaynen yunge.

00:21:16.774 --> 00:21:18.253
iz,

00:21:18.293 --> 00:21:20.295
 hobn mir ongehoybn arbetn,

00:21:20.571 --> 00:21:22.783
un mir hobn genumen an APARTMENT

00:21:23.018 --> 00:21:25.138
oyf EASTERN PARKWAY.

00:21:26.528 --> 00:21:30.681
 CLEVELAND STREET, dakht zikh mir; kh'gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:21:31.287 --> 00:21:33.831
un nokh der, nokh der arbet,

00:21:33.831 --> 00:21:38.227
hobn mir aroysgegang- ye, mir flegn, ⟨⟩, ongreytn,

00:21:38.227 --> 00:21:40.848
az mir veln kumen fun der arbet, zoln mir hobn vos tsu esn,

00:21:40.888 --> 00:21:42.890
un mir hobn aroysgegangen

00:21:43.386 --> 00:21:44.747
oyfn gas.

00:21:45.107 --> 00:21:48.738
 EASTERN PARKWAY hot dortn geven frume,

00:21:48.887 --> 00:21:50.805
un s'hot geven yidn,

00:21:50.845 --> 00:21:53.120
un s⟨'iz⟩, zaynen geshtanen benk;

00:21:53.120 --> 00:21:55.261
ir hot gekent aroysgeyn. un in shap

00:21:55.261 --> 00:21:57.085
hot nisht geven keyn AIR CONDITION,

00:21:57.085 --> 00:21:59.040
hobn mir geven zeyer oysgematert.

00:21:59.434 --> 00:22:02.685
hobn mir zikh gezetst, un mir hobn nokh genumen nokh a khaverte,

00:22:02.742 --> 00:22:05.267
vos mir hobn zikh bakent mit ir in lager,

00:22:05.374 --> 00:22:07.967
az s'zol zayn undz laykhter tsu tsoln di RENT.

00:22:08.513 --> 00:22:10.590
hobn mir zikh,

00:22:11.263 --> 00:22:13.029
 geSHAREt

00:22:13.356 --> 00:22:16.505
di bet mit nokh der khaverte.

00:22:16.663 --> 00:22:18.817
⟨un mir hobn⟩ aroysgegangen khapn dem otem.

00:22:19.482 --> 00:22:21.141
vos hot geven der sof?

00:22:21.141 --> 00:22:22.541
oyf der tsveyter bank

00:22:22.541 --> 00:22:24.504
hot gezesn tsvey bokherim.

00:22:25.270 --> 00:22:27.646
un eyner hot gezogt tsu dem tsveytn,

00:22:27.646 --> 00:22:30.545
"dortn zitsn meydlekh vos zey redn yidish."

00:22:31.986 --> 00:22:33.940
hobn zey ongehoybn redn tsu undz,

00:22:33.940 --> 00:22:36.080
un eyner fun di hot geven mayn man.

00:22:37.285 --> 00:22:38.882
un,

00:22:40.103 --> 00:22:44.033
mir hobn zikh bakent, un er flegt araynkumen tsu undz, vayl er hot zikh gevoynt

00:22:44.052 --> 00:22:45.795
oyf EASTERN PARKWAY,

00:22:45.795 --> 00:22:48.749
un ikh hob zikh gevoynt arayn in EASTERN PARKWAY,

00:22:48.749 --> 00:22:50.914
LINCOLN PLACE hot dos geheysn.

00:22:51.595 --> 00:22:54.136
un mir hobn khasene gehat.

00:22:54.126 --> 00:22:55.571
vi heyst ayer man?

00:22:55.712 --> 00:22:57.579
Arn Shtal. dos iz mayn...

00:22:58.210 --> 00:22:59.756
..-ertsetn april.

00:22:59.914 --> 00:23:01.084
s'zol zayn...

00:23:01.084 --> 00:23:02.541
es iz dokh geven...

00:23:01.163 --> 00:23:02.507
in velkhn yor?

00:23:02.850 --> 00:23:05.510
in, eyn un fuftsik.

00:23:09.613 --> 00:23:16.581
 ikh volt zikh veln a bisl tsukern tsurik. far der tsayt vos ir zayt geven in di kontsentratsye-lager,

00:23:15.928 --> 00:23:16.782
ye.

00:23:16.603 --> 00:23:22.857
hot ir getrofn velkhe nit iz fun di shlekht bavuste natsis vos zaynen gevezn dortn?

00:23:22.560 --> 00:23:25.490
yo, ober ver hot gevust zeyere nemen?

00:23:25.513 --> 00:23:28.623
kh'hob aykh gezogt, mir hobn moyre gehat tsu, mir zaynen geven

00:23:28.623 --> 00:23:32.033
yunge kinder, tseshrokene,

00:23:32.078 --> 00:23:34.431
hungerik, naket,

00:23:34.542 --> 00:23:38.282
derhargete. m'hot gekhapt ibern kop, m'hot gekhapt...

00:23:38.423 --> 00:23:43.800
⟨m-⟩ ir hot nor moyre gehat farn blik, az ir hot nit gevust az zeyer blik

00:23:44.363 --> 00:23:47.056
un ayer blik kenen zikh bagegenen,

00:23:47.056 --> 00:23:49.301
veyst ir nit tsu m'vet aykh nit aroysnemen.

00:23:50.742 --> 00:23:53.826
 ir hot kam, ⟨,⟩ s'hot aykh getreyslt di hent mit di fis

00:23:53.826 --> 00:23:55.395
un ir hot kam moyre gehat,

00:23:55.395 --> 00:23:58.264
ir hot shoyn gebentsht goyml, gedankt got

00:23:58.264 --> 00:24:01.352
az er hot shoyn adurkhgegangen durkh aykh.

00:24:01.997 --> 00:24:04.522
nor ir hot nit gevust vi zey heysn?

00:24:04.512 --> 00:24:07.632
absolut gornisht! absolut.

00:24:08.089 --> 00:24:08.707
OKAY.

00:24:09.810 --> 00:24:12.976
nu, vayter, ir hot khasene gehat shoyn in Amerike.

00:24:11.953 --> 00:24:13.027
yo.

00:24:13.101 --> 00:24:15.609
vi iz ayer lebn vayter ⟨avekgegangen⟩?

00:24:13.168 --> 00:24:14.073
hob ikh...

00:24:14.533 --> 00:24:17.145
 nisht azoy glentsnd.

00:24:19.429 --> 00:24:20.671
mayn man

00:24:21.066 --> 00:24:23.000
hot glaykh gevorn krank,

00:24:23.091 --> 00:24:24.809
vi kh'hob mit im khasene gehat,

00:24:24.809 --> 00:24:26.032
un ikh rekhn

00:24:26.032 --> 00:24:27.678
az er hot shoyn geven krank

00:24:27.678 --> 00:24:29.801
befor, nor er hot nit gevolt dertseyln.

00:24:32.035 --> 00:24:34.442
hob ikh ongehoybn a bisl tsu...

00:24:35.545 --> 00:24:37.668
onheybn zikh doktern mit im.

00:24:37.668 --> 00:24:39.791
m'hot gegangen tsu doktoyrim.

00:24:40.624 --> 00:24:42.086
un,

00:24:42.936 --> 00:24:47.520
m'hot ge- ikh hob gevolt hobn a FAMILY, un s'hot nisht gegangen vayle

00:24:48.808 --> 00:24:50.827
er hot gedarft vern operirt.

00:24:51.745 --> 00:24:56.215
bin ikh gegangen tsu eynem a dokter vos zayn nomen muz ikh bad⟨anken⟩.

00:24:56.215 --> 00:24:57.864
er hot geven azoy vi a malekh.

00:24:57.904 --> 00:24:59.771
azoy vi ikh bin arayn tsu im,

00:25:00.182 --> 00:25:02.132
un er hot gegebn nor a kuk...

00:25:02.443 --> 00:25:04.250
un ikh hob zeyer geveynt.

00:25:05.025 --> 00:25:06.599
ikh hob geklert,

00:25:06.599 --> 00:25:08.886
"far vos? ikh hob azoy fil adurkhgemakht.

00:25:08.886 --> 00:25:10.540
far vos geyt nisht der lebn

00:25:10.540 --> 00:25:12.565
khotsh normal? ikh vil shoyn nisht

00:25:12.565 --> 00:25:15.163
vern raykh in Amerike, ikh vil nisht keyn glikn,

00:25:15.163 --> 00:25:17.523
ober dos darf ikh nokh adurkhmakhn?

00:25:17.833 --> 00:25:19.551
dem khosn hot men geshosn,

00:25:19.551 --> 00:25:22.620
⟨do iz⟩ der man gevorn krank. epes a shlimazl?"

00:25:24.229 --> 00:25:27.125
iz, hot er gegebn a kuk oyf mir.

00:25:29.342 --> 00:25:34.181
zogt er, "veyn nisht." in english. "DON'T CRY.

00:25:34.708 --> 00:25:37.647
HE'S GOING TO BE ALRIGHT. HE'S IN MY HANDS."

00:25:39.332 --> 00:25:41.134
hot er im,

00:25:41.134 --> 00:25:44.456
gemakht ale testn un altsding.

00:25:44.563 --> 00:25:47.617
hot er oysgefunen az er hot gal-shteyner,

00:25:47.820 --> 00:25:49.434
un er darf vern operirt.

00:25:50.487 --> 00:25:54.103
hob ikh nokh moyre gehat: itster ersht khasene gehat, un

00:25:54.103 --> 00:25:55.222
shoyn zol er...

00:25:55.633 --> 00:25:58.512
der sof, m'hot nokh ongehaltn azoy akht khadoshim.

00:25:58.941 --> 00:26:02.676
un nokh di akht khadoshim hot er gemuzt geyn un er hot zikh operirt.

00:26:05.995 --> 00:26:07.440
un,

00:26:07.598 --> 00:26:10.022
keyn, fakh hot er nit gehat,

00:26:10.281 --> 00:26:11.788
vayle er hot geven

00:26:11.788 --> 00:26:13.295
a hebreisher lerer,

00:26:13.572 --> 00:26:14.882
un,

00:26:15.327 --> 00:26:18.783
az ir kent nit di shprakh, ken men aykh nisht gebn keyn JOB.

00:26:19.933 --> 00:26:21.817
hot er gekrign a JOB,

00:26:21.925 --> 00:26:23.589
zeyer shvere arbet:

00:26:23.629 --> 00:26:27.302
er flegt epes darfn pakn shvere skhoyres,

00:26:27.831 --> 00:26:30.255
un s'hot geven zeyer shver far im.

00:26:31.425 --> 00:26:34.524
mir hobn nisht gelitn keyn honik.

00:26:34.547 --> 00:26:36.544
un ikh hob geTRYt tsu,

00:26:36.825 --> 00:26:39.637
in di ergste umshtendn, tsu oyskumen

00:26:39.778 --> 00:26:41.156
vi ikh ken.

00:26:41.753 --> 00:26:44.397
un ot azoy, THANKS GOD, s'iz avek.

00:26:44.858 --> 00:26:47.248
nokh dem iz hob ikh shoyn gehat mayn

00:26:47.271 --> 00:26:48.615
ershte kind.

00:26:49.161 --> 00:26:51.602
dos iz hot geven in,

00:26:51.692 --> 00:26:53.137
dray un fuftsik.

00:26:54.240 --> 00:26:55.499
vi heyst er?

00:26:55.337 --> 00:26:58.160
ikh hob a PICTURE. fun im veys ikh nisht...

00:26:56.755 --> 00:26:58.099
vi heyst er?

00:26:58.160 --> 00:26:59.584
er heyst MURRAY.

00:26:59.826 --> 00:27:02.894
 mir hobn im a nomen gegebn nokh mayn tatn, Mendl.

00:27:02.894 --> 00:27:07.026
hobn mir gevolt, im ⟨amerik- amerikani- -ke⟩zirn,

00:27:07.150 --> 00:27:08.631
iz heyst er

00:27:08.631 --> 00:27:10.265
MURRAY Shtal.

00:27:11.790 --> 00:27:13.302
ir hot nokh kinder?

00:27:11.824 --> 00:27:13.213
UNK

00:27:13.213 --> 00:27:14.568
kh'hob nokh a zun,

00:27:14.895 --> 00:27:16.526
heyst er STUART;

00:27:17.038 --> 00:27:19.040
er iz a nomen nokh mayn mamen.

00:27:19.688 --> 00:27:21.251
un kh'hob a tokhter,

00:27:21.493 --> 00:27:24.879
heyst zi BARBARA, un zi iz a nomen nokh mayn boben.

00:27:25.847 --> 00:27:26.831
hob ikh

00:27:26.831 --> 00:27:28.726
oyfgeshtelt mayn FAMILY.

00:27:28.902 --> 00:27:34.110
zogt mir, ⟨iz⟩ vos hot zikh farnumen ayer mishpokhe shoyn in Amerike, ayer, ayer man un ir?

00:27:33.238 --> 00:27:34.312
mayn man?

00:27:34.875 --> 00:27:38.311
⟨ts-⟩ fun onfang hot er gearbet zeyer shvere arbet,

00:27:38.773 --> 00:27:42.091
un nokh dem hot er gearbet in CHEMICAL BANK.

00:27:43.667 --> 00:27:46.850
er flegt arbetn i⟨UNK⟩

00:27:46.924 --> 00:27:50.965
UNK er flegt, EXPLAINen,

00:27:50.965 --> 00:27:53.932
leyenen briv vos in daytsh, er ken zeyer gut daytsh,

00:27:53.932 --> 00:27:57.229
oder ISRAELI f-, hebreishe briv, oder...

00:27:57.522 --> 00:27:58.733
fun onfang

00:27:58.733 --> 00:28:02.021
hob ikh gevolt, zol er vern a lerer.

00:28:02.854 --> 00:28:06.813
in a hebreishe shule hot men nisht gevolt undz onnemen,

00:28:07.022 --> 00:28:10.121
un m'hot undz nisht gevolt, az mayne kinder

00:28:10.684 --> 00:28:12.714
zoln zayn azoy vi

00:28:12.714 --> 00:28:14.947
s'iz, darf tsu zayn.

00:28:14.970 --> 00:28:16.955
un keyn gelt hobn mir nit gehat.

00:28:17.923 --> 00:28:20.667
UNK nor vos mir hobn gehat iz di

00:28:21.012 --> 00:28:22.609
i- vos mir hobn zikh geshemt

00:28:22.716 --> 00:28:24.161
tsu geyn dertseyln.

00:28:24.842 --> 00:28:28.261
hot er gezogt, "azoy vi ikh'l arbetn, ikh'l aroyshelfn,

00:28:28.808 --> 00:28:33.175
vel ikh ton ANYTHING, un ⟨d-⟩ ikh'l zuntik zey lernen."

00:28:33.175 --> 00:28:36.716
"NO, me darf..." hobn zey avekgegangen in,

00:28:36.807 --> 00:28:40.817
di folkshul, ir veyst ⟨dokh⟩, di amerikaner PUBLIC SCHOOLs,

00:28:41.329 --> 00:28:43.352
un zey hobn zikh dortn gelernt.

00:28:44.485 --> 00:28:46.706
ayere kinder hobn geendikt vos?

00:28:44.502 --> 00:28:45.558
UNK

00:28:46.813 --> 00:28:50.783
 mayn, zun, der elterer, hot

00:28:50.813 --> 00:28:52.565
dray MASTER'S DEGREE.

00:28:52.565 --> 00:28:54.688
er hot azoy: in ekonomik

00:28:54.934 --> 00:28:56.556
a MASTER'S DEGREE;

00:28:56.616 --> 00:29:01.420
er hot in, LANGUAGEs

00:29:01.647 --> 00:29:03.075
a MASTER'S DEGREE;

00:29:03.486 --> 00:29:05.066
un er hot ⟨i-⟩

00:29:05.106 --> 00:29:06.618
kh'rekhn, in...

00:29:07.165 --> 00:29:10.702
ikh ken aykh nit zogn. ikh hob, farshribn...

00:29:09.477 --> 00:29:11.838
BUSINESS ADMINISTRATION UNK?

00:29:11.434 --> 00:29:12.440
vos?

00:29:11.923 --> 00:29:13.925
BUSINESS ADMINISTRATION?

